  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the impact of three different treatment modalities on
      panic symptoms, quality of life and use of health services among individuals consulting an
      emergency department for non cardiac chest pain and having Panic Disorder.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
